title: Data from Picture
_landingPageLine1.comment: We want a sentence split into two fragments. This is the first fragment. For reference the full sentence is ''We're analyzing your image and preparing your data''.
_landingPageLine2.comment: This is the second fragment which follows landingPageLine1. For reference the full sentence is ''We're analyzing your image and preparing your data''.
_helpfulTip.comment: Landing Page text that precedes the actual help text.
helpTipString1: Consider the lighting, camera angles, and cropping the image to focus on the table to help us extract the data more accurately.
_errorStageMessage1.comment: Error message when Data from Picture could not load.
_errorStageMessage2.comment: Error message when Data from Picture could not load.
_error.comment: This is the prefix before the actual error message. The word Error followed by colon.
_lowConfidenceAltText.comment: Shown when user hovers over low confidence table cell.
_previousButtonAltText.comment: Text shown when the user hovers over the Previous button.
_nextButtonAltText.comment: Text shown when the user hovers over the Next button.
_checkIconAltText.comment: Text shown when the user hovers over the Check Icon
_warningIconAltText.comment: Text shown when the user hovers over the Warning Icon
_threePlusItemsRequireReview.comment: Label shown beside warning icon. {0} holds the number
_insertAnywayButton.comment: Button text. User clicks the button if he/she wants to insert cells without reviewing any cells.
itemStillRequireReviewRAI: You are responsible for validating the accuracy of all data.
_threePlusItemsStillRequireReview.commen: Label shown beside warning icon. {0} holds the number
emptyTableHelpMessage: We did not recognize any table data in your image. For best results, crop the image to the edges of the table and try again.
_emptyTableHelpMessage.comment: Help text to show if we couldn't recognize anything from the image
showTooManyLowConfidenceCellsMessage: We are unsure about the data in many cells. You can review them one at a time, or try again with better image quality.
_showTooManyLowConfidenceCellsMessage.co: Text to show when there are too many Low Confidence Cells
_closeWarningButtonAltText.comment: Text read when a Screen reader user focuses the close button on the Warning popup.
infoButtonText: For best results, use good lighting, and crop your image to the edges of the table.
_infoButtonText.comment: Info button text that is shown when the user hovers over the light bulb icon. This is also the Alt text of the button.
infoButtonText0: Click highlighted cells below to edit the values.
_infoButtonText0.comment: Info button text that is shown when the user hovers over the light bulb icon. This is also the Alt text of the button.
infoButtonText2: We cannot recognize some character sets.
_infoButtonText2.comment: Info button text that is shown when the user hovers over the light bulb icon. This is also the Alt text of the button.
_reviewTextBoxAltText.comment: input textbox that allows the user to see and modify values that require a review
_helpDocumentationLink.comment: Link that points to a webpage with tips and documentation on how to use the feature
_thirdPartyNotices.comment: A disclaimer about third party software used in this project.
